Class CollisionInfo

Namespace
Vts.MonteCarlo.PhotonData
Assembly
Vts.dll

Describes a model object designed to hold extra information related to collisions and path length in each region. Inherits from List(OfSubRegionCollisionInfo) as a simple way of having Add() and indexing methods available

public class CollisionInfo : List<SubRegionCollisionInfo>, IList<SubRegionCollisionInfo>, ICollection<SubRegionCollisionInfo>, IReadOnlyList<SubRegionCollisionInfo>, IReadOnlyCollection<SubRegionCollisionInfo>, IEnumerable<SubRegionCollisionInfo>, IList, ICollection, IEnumerable
